  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to evaluate the effectiveness of Mindfulness-based Stress Reduction among Danish&#xD;
      student teachers on their mental well-being. The study is a randomised, controlled trial&#xD;
      including 100 teachers.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
